<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>SentiOwl - Master Cybersecurity Education</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link
href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&
amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link
href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL
@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
 tailwind.config = {
 darkMode: "class",
 theme: {
 extend: {
 colors: {
 "primary": "#0d59f2",
 "dark-bg": "#0F172A",
 "card-bg": "#1E293B",
 "accent-blue": "#0d59f2",
 },
 fontFamily: {
 "display": ["Inter", "sans-serif"]
 },
 borderRadius: {
 "DEFAULT": "0.25rem",
 "lg": "0.5rem",
 "xl": "0.75rem",
 "full": "9999px"
 },
 },
 },
 }
 </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
 .material-symbols-outlined {
 font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
 }
 body {
 font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
 background-color: #0F172A;
 }
 </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark-bg text-slate-200 font-display selection:bg-primary
selection:text-white">
<nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full bg-dark-bg/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b
border-slate-800">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<div class="bg-primary text-white p-1.5 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined block text-[20px]">shield</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">SentiOwl</h1>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">My Path</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Leaderboard</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Curriculum Map</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">About</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Community</a>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<button class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 hover:text-white
transition-colors">Sign In</button>
<button class="px-5 py-2 text-sm font-bold bg-primary text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg
shadow-primary/20 hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all">Sign Up</button>
</div>
</div>
</nav>
<main class="relative">
<section class="relative pt-20 pb-24 overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full -z-10 opacity-20
pointer-events-none">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-[-10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/20 rounded-full
blur-[120px]"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-[-10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/10
rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border
border-primary/30 text-primary text-xs font-bold mb-8">
<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
<span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary
opacity-75"></span>
<span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
</span>
 NEW: ADVANCED MALWARE ANALYSIS TRACK
 </div>
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
 Master Cybersecurity Through <span
class="text-primary">Structured</span>, Practical Learning
 </h1>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
 Build real-world security skills through guided modules, interactive challenges,
and measurable progress. Designed for modern defenders.
 </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
<button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold bg-primary text-white
rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-primary/40 hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform
active:scale-95">
 Start Learning
 </button>
<button class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold border border-slate-700
text-slate-200 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-800 hover:border-slate-600 transition-all
active:scale-95">
 View Curriculum
 </button>
</div>
<div class="mt-16 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl
bg-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm">
<img class="w-full h-auto opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
data-alt="Dashboard showing cybersecurity learning progress and modules"
src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC_kLR8sUY8M_7G29MO-0
sZ02yPBj4hVpa8Vp1y1tZL8Y2tsZzxAnvhm9mUrtp1p80cwLfwmmY0nOggxp6hNiLCZX
wDDzMizFTeWh0hV9qE-0bqDmg8JtjVzCZuGBrXkwq4lB_rl9T7zit6P_jy3Ug0Z-XfTtE5O
fXq2cFoMaCMYs6qN3Vnoqan4lug4wgXNJ1wCOL9uYde2ohdUXuE8b48gwTFg6TGEj
Kx6g3Rpe0w0i-66L5Ql7J8Jb5Vs0OTtU2J3Qo_Gste6D0"/>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-900/30 border-y border-slate-800/50">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Everything you need to level up</h2>
<p class="text-slate-400">Professional-grade education without the academic
bureaucracy.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div class="p-8 bg-card-bg border border-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl
hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center
text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">school</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Structured Curriculum</h3>
<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
 Expert-led paths designed to guide you from foundational security
concepts to advanced enterprise defense architectures.
 </p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-card-bg border border-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl
hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center
text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">terminal</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Interactive Challenges</h3>
<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
Engage with hands-on labs in a safe, sandboxed environment to test
your theoretical knowledge against live, real-world scenarios.
 </p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-card-bg border border-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl
hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center
text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">leaderboard</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Competitive Leaderboard</h3>
<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
 Track your progress, earn industry-recognized badges, and climb the
ranks against a global community of high-performing learners.
 </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="py-24">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight text-white">Ready to secure your
future?</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-10">
 Join over 15,000 students mastering the art of cybersecurity. Start your first
module today—no credit card required.
 </p>
<div class="flex justify-center">
<button class="px-12 py-4 text-lg font-bold bg-primary text-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl
shadow-primary/30 hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
 Get Started Now
 </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
<footer class="bg-dark-bg py-16 border-t border-slate-800">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8 mb-12">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<div class="bg-primary/20 text-primary p-1.5 rounded-lg flex items-center
justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined block text-[18px]">shield</span>
</div>
<span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">SentiOwl</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Terms of Service</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Contact Us</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors"
href="#">Enterprise</a>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-800
text-slate-400 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
</a>
<a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-800
text-slate-400 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">code</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800/50 text-center">
<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">© 2024 SentiOwl Inc. Empowering the next
generation of security professionals.</p>
</div>
</div>
</footer>
</body></html>
